asing ionized mass fraction should be\nsensitive to the spatial distribution and the luminosity of ionizing sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jun 2008 20:05:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Dec 2008 07:21:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
